h2. Setup Instructions

h3. Install the VS Code Extension

Install the TGS Flow extension in VS Code.

h3. Configure Settings

Open the Command Palette and configure:

* Jira Base URL
* GitHub Token
* Jira Token
* Jira Project Keys

h3. Install Git Hooks

Run the command:

{code}
TGS Flow: Install Git Hook
{code}

This enables:

* pre commit validation
* post commit reconciliation

h3. Confirm Commands

Verify the following commands are available:

* Install Git Hook
* Reconcile Work
* Scan TODOs to Jira
* Solution Doc to Backlog

h3. Run Initial Test

Use a sample document or notes to confirm the workflow works.

