h2. Core Workflow

h3. Primary Use Case

Typical workflow:

# Team holds a design or planning session

# Notes or a solution document are created

# The document is used to generate Jira backlog items

# Backlog is reviewed and refined in Jira

# Work is assigned to engineers

# Engineers begin implementation

# GitHub commits update Jira automatically

# Jira reflects real execution

---

h2. Key Commands

h3. Install Git Hook

Installs repository hooks enabling automated validation and reconciliation.

h3. Reconcile Work

Manually scans commits and reconciles them with Jira issues.

h3. Scan TODOs to Jira

Finds TODO comments in code and proposes Jira issues.

h3. Solution Doc to Backlog

Generates candidate backlog items from a solution document.

